    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six. This unit delivers precise throttle response via individual throttle bodies and a tactile ZF 6-speed manual gearbox. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain torsional rigidity. The factory limited-slip differential ensures optimal torque distribution, while the suspension geometry remains true for sharp turn-in. A well-maintained example offering the peak of analog driving dynamics and mechanical transparency.",
