      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a seamless blend of luxury and performance. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated metallic charcoal that retains a deep, lustrous gloss, with only a few minor stone chips expected from light, respectful use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seating is supple and free of cracks, while the high-grade plastics and wood trim show no signs of sun fading or wear. All electronic systems\u2014including the navigation, heated seats, and premium audio\u2014operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers power smoothly, backed by a complete service history that confirms it has never missed a scheduled maintenance interval. The transmission is crisp, the suspension is silent, and the tires have approximately 75% tread remaining. This is a turn-key vehicle for a discerning buyer who wants the quality of a high-end car without the 'new' price tag.",
